 Ring and The Cradle Will Rock; and an account of Rosenbaum's work as consultant on the 1998 re-editing of Touch of Evil, based on a studio memo by Welles.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMotion picturesvBiography. 0aMotion picturesxAnalysis, appreciation. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  aamerican director.  abiographical.  acareer.  achimes at midnight.  acinema.  acreative control.  acreative process.  adon quixote.  af for fake.  afilm criticism.  afilm director.  afilm studies.  afilms.  aheart of darkness.  ahollywood.  ainnovation.  amovie studies.  amovies.  aorson welles.  aothello.  apersonal interviews.  araising kane.  astudio memo.  athe big brass ring.  athe cradle will rock.  athe ultimate auteur.  atouch of evil.  aunfinished films.  aunfinished work.  awelles canon.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094071040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520940710423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520940710/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles